"Allow font files (.woff2, .woff, .ttf, .otf) to be uploaded to the media "
"library. This enables custom font support for your site."
msgstr "允許將字體檔案（.woff2、.woff、.ttf、.otf）上傳到媒體庫。這將為您的網站啟用自訂字體支援。"

